init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I look down at the bee, and it looks back at me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I look around, and I notice that I'm not in my bedroom anymore.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A voice booms from the ceiling, "Welcome, your majesty!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Your majesty, you have been chosen to lead the bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I look around the room, and I notice that there are thousands of bees surrounding me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I am also starting to feel a little bit more confident about my new role as queen.
